com.unimelb.swen30006.mailroom

Class MailSorter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.unimelb.swen30006.mailroom.MailSorter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Stepable

    public class MailSorter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Stepable
    A MailSorting computer that takes a MailSource, and a Sorting Strategy and will use that strategy to continuously sort mail into boxes until their is none left in the MailSource. Works with delivery bots to clear storage and deliver mail
